# 「 Axentra v1.2.0 」

### Added
- /anvil - Open an anvil without a physical block
- /workbench - Open a crafting table without a physical block
- /cartography - Open a cartography table without a physical block
- /grindstone - Open a grindstone without a physical block
- /loom - Open a loom without a physical block
- /smithingtable - Open a smithing table without a physical block
- /stonecutter - Open a stonecutter without a physical block
- /enderchest - Open your ender chest from anywhere
- /fly [player] - Toggle flight for yourself or another player
- /hat - Place the item in your hand on your head
- /ping [player] - Check your ping or another player's ping
- /suicide - Kill yourself
- /time <set|add> <day|noon|night|midnight|ticks> - Set or add to the world time
- /weather <clear|rain|storm> - Set the weather
- /clearwarns <player> - Clear all warnings for a player

### Other
- Time shortcuts: /day, /noon, /night, /midnight
- Weather shortcuts: /sun, /sky, /rain, /storm
- /axentra information now shows the support Discord link

Download: https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/axentra.133221/ @Updates

