# 「 Axentra v1.1.0 」

### Added
- /mute <player> [reason] - Mute a player from the chat
- /unmute <player> - Unmute a player
- /warn <player> [reason] - Warn a player
- /warns [player] - View warnings for a player
- /heal [player] - Heal yourself or another player
- /feed [player] - Feed yourself or another player
- /banip <player|ip> [reason] - Ban a player's IP address
- /unbanip <ip> - Unban an IP address
- /tempban <player> <duration> [reason] - Temporarily ban a player
- /tempbanip <player|ip> <duration> [reason] - Temporarily ban an IP address

### Other
- Warn punishments system - automatically kick, mute, tempban or ban at set warn counts
- Duration format support (e.g. 1d2h30m) for tempban commands

Download: https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/axentra.133221/ @Updates